hs_fulda.JavaParser

Class Analyzer

  • java.lang.Object
    • hs_fulda.JavaParser.Analyzer

  • public class Analyzer
extends java.lang.Object

    Analyzer

    The Application do an analysis of a java code with a constraint stated in the JSON file. If all the required constraints are met, no error is displayed on the screen, else an error is displayed whenever the rules specified in the constraint file (JSON) are negated.
    Since:
    20-06-2018
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Ammar Hasan, Chukwuebuka Ezelu, Wajahat Ali
